    /tmp: This directory stores temporary files that are generated by the running applications and processes
    /boot: This directory stores the required file to start the linux operating system
    /home: It's a dedicate space for the each user. User can store their personal and dedicated files and applications
    /var: This directory is used to store the files which are dynamic in size and content. This will collect the data from the runnings applications like collects logs of the application while it running.

